#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_pong.html.heex:35
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Ball angle depends on where it hits the paddle — center gives a shallow bounce, edges give steep angles (up to 60 degrees)"
